name: Crossover Monokini - Small
description:
School pride doesn't have to stop when you hit the sand!

Look fabulous and show your colors on the beach with this gorgeous orange and white monokini crossover!

This suit was featured by Sports Illustrated in 2010 in the worn by 2010 cover model, Brooklyn Decker! 


Free shipping on additional suits.
